videos.description: Tulane's Justin McMillan connects with Darnell Mooney with a 17-yard touchdown pass to take the lead over Cincinnati.
videos.headline: McMillan finds Mooney for 17-yard TD

videos.description: Desmond Ridder connects with Kahlil Lewis on a 25-yard touchdown pass.
videos.headline: Cincinnati QB Ridder throws 25-yard TD to Lewis

videos.description: Darius Bradwell sneaks through the Cincinnati defense for a Tulane touchdown.
videos.headline: Tulane's Bradwell runs 19 yards for TD

videos.description: Cincinnati quarterback Desmond Ridder picks up his first rushing touchdown of the day to put the Bearcats up 24-14 over Tulane.
videos.headline: Ridder bolts 28 yards for TD

videos.description: Desmond Ridder throws between two defenders to find Kahlil Lewis for their second touchdown connection of the day.
videos.headline: Ridder makes second connection with Lewis for TD

videos.description: Tavion Thomas takes the handoff and jets 25 yards for the touchdown to put Cincinnati up 37-14 over Tulane.
videos.headline: Thomas rushes 25 yards for Bearcat TD

videos.description: Tulane quarterback Justin McMillan locates Terren Encalade who tiptoes in the endzone for a 14-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: McMillan targets Encalade for 14-yard Tulane TD
